  "name": "ENRICHPersonalHealthDevice",
  "title": "ENRICH-mHealth Personal Health Device",
  "status": "draft",
  "description": "Profile for a personal health device (wearable / mHealth / IoT sensor, e.g. smartwatch, ring, patch, scale) that captures ENRICH-mHealth observations. Modeled after the gematik HDDT `hddt-personal-health-device` (Health Device Data Transfer, § 374a SGB V), adapted for the ENRICH research context: the BfARM/HIIS registry requirement of HDDT is intentionally NOT imposed, and manufacturer/type are captured to identify the wearable.",
